                <p class="text-sm dark:text-primary-200/60 text-primary-950/60" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>短按快捷键，开始语音输入</p>
              </div>
              <div class="items-center justify-center rounded-full absolute h-9 w-9 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary-50/95 dark:bg-primary-950/95 dark:ring-primary-200/20 dark:text-primary-400 hidden md:flex right-0 ring-1 ring-primary-900/10 shadow-sm text-primary-500 top-1/2 translate-x-1/2 z-10" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                  <path d="M10 7l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt stroke-width="2.2"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="items-center flex flex-col gap-4 cursor-default dark:hover:bg-primary-900/60 group hover:bg-white/60 md:p-12 p-8 transition-colors relative" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
              <div class="relative h-20 w-20" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                <div class="duration-500 transition-transform absolute bg-primary-600/5 dark:bg-primary-400/10 group-hover:scale-110 inset-0 rounded-2xl" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt></div>
                <div class="items-center flex justify-center absolute inset-0" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                  <svg class="dark:text-primary-400 text-primary-600 h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                    <path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
                <h3 class="dark:text-primary-200 text-primary-950 font-semibold mb-2 text-lg" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>本地识别</h3>
                <p class="text-sm dark:text-primary-200/60 text-primary-950/60" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>本地 ASR 引擎，隐私数据不出设备</p>
              </div>
              <div class="items-center justify-center rounded-full absolute h-9 w-9 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary-50/95 dark:bg-primary-950/95 dark:ring-primary-200/20 dark:text-primary-400 hidden md:flex right-0 ring-1 ring-primary-900/10 shadow-sm text-primary-500 top-1/2 translate-x-1/2 z-10" data-astro-cid-ewxirvlt>
