            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4" data-astro-cid-ludp2yfi>
              <h3 class="font-medium dark:text-primary-200 text-primary-950 text-3xl tracking-tight" data-astro-cid-ludp2yfi>语音输入</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed dark:text-primary-200/70 text-primary-950/70 text-base" data-astro-cid-ludp2yfi>
                短按快捷键开始语音输入，支持本地和云端语音识别模型，可自由配置。内置自动结构化与口语过滤，让口语瞬间变文章。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="items-center flex justify-center dark:hover:bg-primary-400/10 hover:bg-primary-500/10 bg-primary-500/5 dark:bg-primary-400/5 group min-h-[300px] p-6 rounded-2xl sm:p-8 transition-colors" data-astro-cid-ludp2yfi>
